versionHistory.releaseNotes: In this release we fixed various bugs and issues affecting iOS 7.0 users.

In this release, we’ve made it easier for you to find who you’re looking for.
• Now you can sort your contacts by first or last name
• Then, quickly jump to a name that begins with a specific letter
• We also fixed various bugs related to sorting, filtering, and searching for contacts

- Improved stability and responsiveness
- Fixed the missing message and subject for birthday notifications 
- Addressed a few iPhone 6 specific layout issues

— We’ve made it easier to get around the app with a new navigation menu.
— New for iOS8: Get easy access to the most important updates about your network, right from your Notification Center 
— Enjoy a smoother, faster experience on iOS8
— We’ve fixed some bugs, including:
     * Authentication issues
     * Unresponsiveness when signing in
     * Intermittent crashes

• Get updates when your connections publish a new post, so you can share your thoughts
• Search for anyone on LinkedIn by name, so you can easily add new connections
• Access relevant Help Center topics directly from the app
• Bug fixes
- Fixed a bug affecting some users when signing in
LinkedIn Connected is a reimagined and redesigned version of LinkedIn Contacts. It has all the same great features, but with much more focus on strengthening your relationships.

- A beautiful new app icon
- Bug fixes and performance improvements

We've made some improvements. Now it's even easier to stay in touch and strengthen your relationships.

• Each To Do item is now easier to read, showing you more information about your opportunities to reach out
• See when your contacts are mentioned in the news and celebrate their success by sharing the news with your network
• Quickly swipe to dismiss any To Do item you don't want to act on

• Improving the launch experience for users by taking them directly to their relationship opportunities
• Performance improvements and bug fixes

• We made a fix for users who were experiencing issues with the To-do tab not refreshing daily

---

We've made huge improvements to the app to ensure that you get the best Contacts experience possible. Now you can:

• View work anniversaries and location changes for all your contacts
• Comment directly on LinkedIn for job changes and work anniversaries
• Add one-time and recurring reminders for your contacts
• Edit/delete previous Notes and How Your Met

description.standard:
The new LinkedIn Connected app is a fast, easy, and smarter way to strengthen your professional relationships. Why is that important? Because most opportunities come from the people you already know, and fostering genuine relationships can help you be more successful. Connected gives you relevant updates about the people you know, so you can reach out when it matters most.

So invest in your connections today for opportunities tomorrow.

• Know when to reach out. Get notified about jobs changes, birthdays, work anniversaries, & more.
• Focus on the people who matter with relevant, timely updates.
• Make a great impression and start better conversations with pre-meeting intelligence. 
• Build stronger relationships in just a few minutes a day.

softwareInfo.requirementsString: Requires iOS 7.0 or later. Compatible with iPhone, iPad, and iPod touch. This app is optimized for iPhone 5, iPhone 6, and iPhone 6 Plus.
